title: *Massive 6-Bedroom & 2.5-Bathroom Dplx Apt w/Private Backyard* 700 #1
posting_body: ["*I Can Show You ALL the Available Units in This Building And ALL of Rentopia's Properties ||", 'NO BROKER FEE*', 'We are the exclusive brokers for this building', '*Massive 6-Bedroom & 2.5-Bathroom Duplex Apartment w/Private Backyard*', 'The pictures are showing the actual available unit - I took them myself!', '*Offering 2 weeks FREE for ASAP lease start date!*', '$7,000 Gross + 2 weeks free ($6,708 Net)', '*The Apartment Features:*', '*Duplex Layout* / 6 Queen-Size Bedrooms / Sunny Living Space that Can Accommodate a Full Set of Furniture & a Large Dining Table / Another Living Space Downstairs that Can be Used as an Office Space or a TV Nook / Floor-to-Ceiling Windows / Great Natural Light All Throughout the Apartment / *Huge Private Backyard* / *2 Bathrooms with a Deep Soaking Tub* /', 'Another Half Bathroom / *Washer & Dryer in Unit* / AC Unit in Each Room / L-Shaped Kitchen with Full-Size Stainless Steel Appliances including a Dishwasher & Built-in Microwave / High Ceilings / Hardwood Floors / Video Intercom /', 'A Step Away from the J & M & G Trains at Flushing Ave Station /', '*Good credit history 700+ and a combined annual income of $280,000+ (40x times the rent) are required / Personal guarantors are welcome!', '"Insurent" is accepted on a case by case basis*']
